      "created_at": "2023-09-25T15:56:03.832Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi!</p>\n<p>I observe an issue with iOs app that keeps controlling resistance of my Kickr Bike even if no workout is running in the app. It feels like after a workout is done it stays connected to the bike for indefinite time and sets it to the mode and the resistance the workout ended with.</p>\n<p>I have to close the app for the interference to stop.</p>\n<p>Alex.</p>",
