      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2023-09-25T21:02:20.608Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Thanks so much for the reply.  It\u2019s interesting no one else has complained.  When you said it before I was thinking you were likely right that its a good idea.  I guess we also had problems with reconnecting to devices in the past so we were probably trying to solve that problem as well.  Let us look at this.  I agree with you, especially since you say that no other apps do this <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\">  Meaning I believe you.  I never close apps either. But I also pretty much only use TD <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"></p>",
