      "cooked": "<p>I need to confirm with <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/loovery\">@Loovery</a>  but I am not sure why we would keep sending power targets after the workout is done.  That sounds like a bug to me.  I don\u2019t need that as a setting as I don\u2019t see any reason to do that. <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\">   If we are doing that seems like a simple fix. I will let you know soon.</p>",
