      "cooked": "<p>I tried the latest version of the app and it still does the same as above (keeps sending erg mode and power targets after the session is done), plus when I run it in ERG mode it dips the power by 10-20watts every ~20 seconds now. Here is the workout I did earlier today:<br>\n<a href=\"https://app.trainerday.com/calendar?event_id=65385dfc0ada0466d7bb39eb\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Trainer Day - Workout: VO2MAX_LONG #5</a></p>\n<p>This is now completely unusable\u2026</p>",
