      "created_at": "2023-10-31T15:35:07.375Z",
      "cooked": "<p>In Zwift you want to disconnect the \u201ccontrollable\u201d or even free ride from Zwift will send updates as well.  You could try running our app without zwift and you might not see these issues.</p>",
